c3262030cc","tid":991114,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:43:02.000Z","msg":"支那狗以為大學係垃圾會/香港政府咁咁易被你入侵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那狗返支那啦<br />\n2019年度周年大選中央諮詢大會第一日<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UgK7W8UaX0M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUgK7W8UaX0M&d=eHGin6srybVV6v6u95%2FlF%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=83a870a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UgK7W8UaX0M</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學學生會校園電視早前訪問「蒼傲」三名成員，三人的政治立場與近年的港大學生會大相逕庭，包括認為政府取消議員資格的判決過程屬公平，並有足夠理據支持政府所作的判決，故對DQ議員沒有任何特別意見，又形容人大釋法是「成功的新詮釋」。片段一出後，三人被學生和網民被批評為「染紅」和親建制，甚至被學生促三人退選。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190121/s00001/1548065609276/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3%E3%80%8C%E8%92%BC%E5%82%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%A4%AB%E5%A5%AA%E6%95%99%E5%93%A1%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AD%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E7%A8%B1%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%85%B6%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%85%89%E8%AD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190121%2Fs00001%2F1548065609276%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2596%25A3%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2592%25BC%25E5%2582%25B2%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AD%259C&d=eHGin6srybVV6v6u95%2FlF%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2a7b6abd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fi